rComments: He is very rude and unprofessional. Doesn't show up to class the first 3 weeks and expects us to be ok with it. He reads off his computer the entire lecture and does not properly answer our questions in class. Do not take any of his classes !

I was really excited to take Social Deviance, that was until I went to class. He doesn't use power point, instead he writes on the board and reads out loud from the course pack. His lectures are very boring and hard to sit through.  He is a tough grader. His expectations are unclear and when prompted for more information he remains vague. AVOID.
Je vous recommande de ne pas le prendre car il est vraiment dur a suivre et se mêle dans ses propos.
La technologie ce n'est pas sa force, mais pour le reste il est bien haha!! Il donne les questions d'examen à l'avance c'est merveilleux ;) les lectures sont complètement inutiles!!
